🟢 When to use Comparable
👉 Use Comparable when:

1️⃣ Natural / default sorting chahiye
2️⃣ Sirf ONE sorting logic enough ho
3️⃣ Tum class modify kar sakte ho
4️⃣ Sorting fixed rehni hai (runtime change nahi)

📌 Example use-case

Student → sort by rollNo

Employee → sort by id

String → alphabetical order


..................................................

🔵 When to use Comparator
👉 Use Comparator when:

1️⃣ Multiple sorting logics chahiye
2️⃣ Runtime pe sorting decide karni ho
3️⃣ Class modify nahi kar sakte (3rd-party / library class)
4️⃣ Sorting rules frequently change hote ho

📌 Example use-case

Sort Student by age / name / marks

Sort Employee by salary / department / name

UI sorting options (dropdown based)